OL,5, A teacher who has been the target of   
OL,6, abuse on TikTok says others in the     
OL,7, profession are being "pushed over the  
OL,8, edge" by online harassment.            
OL,10,FTom Rogers is one of dozens of teachers
OL,11,Fwho have reported harassment on social 
OL,12,Fmedia in recent weeks, some of whom    
OL,13,Fhave signed off sick.                  
OL,15,FThe posts often feature footage from   
OL,16,Flearning resources used by teachers    
OL,17,Fduring lockdowns.                      
OL,19,FTikTok says it is taking extra measures
OL,20,Fto remove videos targeting teachers.   
